request.description:
Login as Super Admin.
Auto-saves → {{adminToken}}

Super Admin can: approve/reject at any stage, review thumbnails, withdraw any video.

Login as Medical Affairs.
Auto-saves → {{medicalToken}}

Medical Affairs can: approve/reject VIDEO TRACK at MEDICAL_REVIEW.

Login as Content Approver.
Auto-saves → {{approverToken}}

Content Approver can: APPROVE ONLY at AWAITING_APPROVER stage. Cannot reject.

